‘I feel like I’m in a movie’ is what Brandon, my executive assistant, keeps saying while exploring Abu Dhabi with me. I mean, I can see why!

When Brandon joined our team earlier this year, he said that he’s biggest dream would be to travel the world (he hasn’t left the US until 2 weeks ago) and so I’m on a mission of making it happen.

It’s been so touching to explore Abu Dhabi (I know really well) with someone who’s here for the first time and is enchanted by every detail. 

It’s our last day today so check out my stories to see a Michelin star charcoal pizza we just had! 🫠
